  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the impact of nephrectomy in renal cancer on blood pressure and renal
      function. The patients will have a follow-up of their blood pressure and renal function until
      6 months after their operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
